  "detailed_description": "<h1>Steam Deck Optimization</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/7b77cbd960e21d71e848745fc5171557.avif?t=1771929797\" width=800 height=224 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A collector's dream! A compilation consisting of  two cult-classic Indonesian horror titles: <strong>DreadOut and DreadOut: Keepers of The Dark</strong>, remastered and bundled in one package for a smoother, modern gameplay experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/2ebf8ef6708c2699b49be990eb486b1d.avif?t=1771929797\" width=616 height=29 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Originally released between 2014 and 2016, both titles have been enhanced with improved visuals, controls, and overall performance. Now available on PC in one unified launcher, with console versions also supported.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/c312c463fc3029d2754008a66c3faf02.avif?t=1771929797\" width=616 height=29 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/72e25f9e6c9f7b6f65f259e8f4b63e7d.poster.avif?t=1771929797\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/72e25f9e6c9f7b6f65f259e8f4b63e7d.webm?t=1771929797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/72e25f9e6c9f7b6f65f259e8f4b63e7d.mp4?t=1771929797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Both <i>DreadOut</i> and <i>Keepers of the Dark</i> are bundled in one launcher and remastered together. Since they share the same engine, both games were upgraded to the latest Unity version with improved visuals, controls, and performance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/5e4be10e377fc2422cf968e890e95380.avif?t=1771929797\" width=616 height=29 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Improved Lighting System using post-processing.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/a5267161113f636dd59dd641a296f9ec.poster.avif?t=1771929797\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/a5267161113f636dd59dd641a296f9ec.webm?t=1771929797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/a5267161113f636dd59dd641a296f9ec.mp4?t=1771929797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Better game textures and smoother shaders.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/34ee99b3e5518bbb1c2498c035e8ca4f.poster.avif?t=1771929797\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/34ee99b3e5518bbb1c2498c035e8ca4f.webm?t=1771929797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/34ee99b3e5518bbb1c2498c035e8ca4f.mp4?t=1771929797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upscaled resolution of all cutscenes</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/45f94add38c433da4c4073cc96a61305.poster.avif?t=1771929797\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/45f94add38c433da4c4073cc96a61305.webm?t=1771929797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/45f94add38c433da4c4073cc96a61305.mp4?t=1771929797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/61d4b09fa77aaae0b2d0b70f65c99c3e.avif?t=1771929797\" width=616 height=29 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Loading takes 3x shorter duration.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/f1f7e8069e9d2cdbbfdfcda646ecd7fd.poster.avif?t=1771929797\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/f1f7e8069e9d2cdbbfdfcda646ecd7fd.webm?t=1771929797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/f1f7e8069e9d2cdbbfdfcda646ecd7fd.mp4?t=1771929797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/28dad34bc93eaf8e8caf68210d627b85.avif?t=1771929797\" width=616 height=29 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enhanced Graphics: Ambient Occlusion, Motion Blur, Bloom, and SMAA.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New Brightness System: Enhanced lighting using post-processing.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Updated UI: Added a full-screen warning menu for consistency.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fixed several enemies' behavior.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fixed glitches that only occur in modern devices.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Analog input now affects animations properly.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/8c8d2fcecd88f453930123416646a972.avif?t=1771929797\" width=616 height=29 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Better aiming</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tuned sensitivity,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Smoother DSLR control</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tighter movement and reduced drifting.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/ef70114d73967fc7afd4e75c5cc44be3.avif?t=1771929797\" width=616 height=29 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/f0f3d63b05aee96fe7e1356d72815dfb.avif?t=1771929797\" width=600 height=230 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DreadOut: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traditional Chinese</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Portuguese</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DreadOut: Keepers of The Dark</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traditional Chinese</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Polish</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hungarian</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Russian</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spanish</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >German</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Portuguese</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/877eafdb6de7d6fe2352d923351013f7.avif?t=1771929797\" width=616 height=29 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/ba322f1c4891417df147a585df9e514a.avif?t=1771929797\" width=620 height=349 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DreadOut Remastered Collection is Steam Deck Verified! If you own the console, you can take and enjoy it anywhere!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>***</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About DreadOut</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DreadOut is a third person supernatural horror game where you play as Linda, a high school student trapped in an old, abandoned town. Equipped with her trusty smartphone and an SLR camera, she will battle against terrifying encounters and solve mysterious puzzles which will ultimately determine her fate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help her overcome the challenges that will stand before her. Survive the Dread!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When a group of high school students went astray from a field trip, they came across something totally unexpected. A town long forgotten, trapped in a peaceful state of slumber. What they did not realize was what lurks within. And what seemed like an innocent stroll turns into disaster as the secluded town reveals its dark and terrible secrets. The presence of sinister forces from beyond their realm of existence.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It all comes down to Linda. She will experience stirrings of unfamiliar powers, emerging from within her. These newfound abilities might just be the only way she can save her own life and those of her friends.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About DreadOut: Keepers of the Dark</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DreadOut: Keepers of the Dark is a new standalone horror game that takes place in the DreadOut universe. In this missing chapter, you will help Linda face the challenges of the DreadOut world with even more dangers lurking within.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow the event in which Linda was transported by The Mysterious Lady in Red into The Mirror Realm. A portal of worlds that connects it to 8 haunted dominions where 13+ horrific ghosts are ready to greet her in the most terrifying way possible. They will stop at nothing to thwart your main objective: To survive!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So, get your smart phone and SLR camera ready and choose your path wisely. The doors you open will decide the outcome of Linda’s fate.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A collector's dream! A compilation consisting of  two cult-classic Indonesian horror titles: <strong>DreadOut and DreadOut: Keepers of The Dark</strong>, remastered and bundled in one package for a smoother, modern gameplay experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/2ebf8ef6708c2699b49be990eb486b1d.avif?t=1771929797\" width=616 height=29 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Originally released between 2014 and 2016, both titles have been enhanced with improved visuals, controls, and overall performance. Now available on PC in one unified launcher, with console versions also supported.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/c312c463fc3029d2754008a66c3faf02.avif?t=1771929797\" width=616 height=29 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/72e25f9e6c9f7b6f65f259e8f4b63e7d.poster.avif?t=1771929797\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/72e25f9e6c9f7b6f65f259e8f4b63e7d.webm?t=1771929797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/72e25f9e6c9f7b6f65f259e8f4b63e7d.mp4?t=1771929797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Both <i>DreadOut</i> and <i>Keepers of the Dark</i> are bundled in one launcher and remastered together. Since they share the same engine, both games were upgraded to the latest Unity version with improved visuals, controls, and performance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/5e4be10e377fc2422cf968e890e95380.avif?t=1771929797\" width=616 height=29 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Improved Lighting System using post-processing.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/a5267161113f636dd59dd641a296f9ec.poster.avif?t=1771929797\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/a5267161113f636dd59dd641a296f9ec.webm?t=1771929797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/a5267161113f636dd59dd641a296f9ec.mp4?t=1771929797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Better game textures and smoother shaders.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/34ee99b3e5518bbb1c2498c035e8ca4f.poster.avif?t=1771929797\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/34ee99b3e5518bbb1c2498c035e8ca4f.webm?t=1771929797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/34ee99b3e5518bbb1c2498c035e8ca4f.mp4?t=1771929797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upscaled resolution of all cutscenes</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/45f94add38c433da4c4073cc96a61305.poster.avif?t=1771929797\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/45f94add38c433da4c4073cc96a61305.webm?t=1771929797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/45f94add38c433da4c4073cc96a61305.mp4?t=1771929797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/61d4b09fa77aaae0b2d0b70f65c99c3e.avif?t=1771929797\" width=616 height=29 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Loading takes 3x shorter duration.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/f1f7e8069e9d2cdbbfdfcda646ecd7fd.poster.avif?t=1771929797\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/f1f7e8069e9d2cdbbfdfcda646ecd7fd.webm?t=1771929797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/f1f7e8069e9d2cdbbfdfcda646ecd7fd.mp4?t=1771929797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/28dad34bc93eaf8e8caf68210d627b85.avif?t=1771929797\" width=616 height=29 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enhanced Graphics: Ambient Occlusion, Motion Blur, Bloom, and SMAA.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New Brightness System: Enhanced lighting using post-processing.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Updated UI: Added a full-screen warning menu for consistency.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fixed several enemies' behavior.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fixed glitches that only occur in modern devices.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Analog input now affects animations properly.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/8c8d2fcecd88f453930123416646a972.avif?t=1771929797\" width=616 height=29 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Better aiming</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tuned sensitivity,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Smoother DSLR control</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tighter movement and reduced drifting.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/ef70114d73967fc7afd4e75c5cc44be3.avif?t=1771929797\" width=616 height=29 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/f0f3d63b05aee96fe7e1356d72815dfb.avif?t=1771929797\" width=600 height=230 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DreadOut: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traditional Chinese</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Portuguese</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DreadOut: Keepers of The Dark</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traditional Chinese</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Polish</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hungarian</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Russian</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spanish</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >German</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Portuguese</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/877eafdb6de7d6fe2352d923351013f7.avif?t=1771929797\" width=616 height=29 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500800/extras/ba322f1c4891417df147a585df9e514a.avif?t=1771929797\" width=620 height=349 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DreadOut Remastered Collection is Steam Deck Verified! If you own the console, you can take and enjoy it anywhere!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>***</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About DreadOut</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DreadOut is a third person supernatural horror game where you play as Linda, a high school student trapped in an old, abandoned town. Equipped with her trusty smartphone and an SLR camera, she will battle against terrifying encounters and solve mysterious puzzles which will ultimately determine her fate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help her overcome the challenges that will stand before her. Survive the Dread!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When a group of high school students went astray from a field trip, they came across something totally unexpected. A town long forgotten, trapped in a peaceful state of slumber. What they did not realize was what lurks within. And what seemed like an innocent stroll turns into disaster as the secluded town reveals its dark and terrible secrets. The presence of sinister forces from beyond their realm of existence.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It all comes down to Linda. She will experience stirrings of unfamiliar powers, emerging from within her. These newfound abilities might just be the only way she can save her own life and those of her friends.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About DreadOut: Keepers of the Dark</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DreadOut: Keepers of the Dark is a new standalone horror game that takes place in the DreadOut universe. In this missing chapter, you will help Linda face the challenges of the DreadOut world with even more dangers lurking within.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow the event in which Linda was transported by The Mysterious Lady in Red into The Mirror Realm. A portal of worlds that connects it to 8 haunted dominions where 13+ horrific ghosts are ready to greet her in the most terrifying way possible. They will stop at nothing to thwart your main objective: To survive!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So, get your smart phone and SLR camera ready and choose your path wisely. The doors you open will decide the outcome of Linda’s fate.</p>",
